ASN Brand Identity for highcharter Package

Source: R/asn_theme.R
asn_theme.Rd

ASN Brand Identity for highcharter Package

Usage

asn_theme

Format

An object of class hc_theme of length 8.

Value

Custom highcharter theme with ASN Brand Identity

Examples

library(highcharter)
highchart() |>
  hc_add_series(
    data = iris,
    type = "scatter",
    hcaes(
      x = Sepal.Length,
      y = Sepal.Width,
      group = Species
    )
  ) |>
  hc_add_theme(
    asn_theme
  )
